For An Act To Be Entitled
9
10 AN ACT TO PROHIBIT A PERSON REQUIRED TO REGISTER AS A
11 SEX OFFENDER FROM ENTERING A WATER PARK, SWIMMING
12 AREA, OR CHILDREN'S PLAYGROUND OF A PUBLIC PARK; AND
